   </front>
   <middle>
      <section title="Tests" anchor="tests">
         <t>This section contains test cases for &lt;xref/&gt;, testing 6 different types of targets. Each target is tested for all possible values of the @format attribute, and for &lt;xref/&gt; elements with and without content.</t>
         <section title="Tests for section-anchor" anchor="section-anchor-tests">
            <t>&lt;xref target="section-anchor"/&gt;: <xref target="section-anchor"/>
            </t>
            <t>&lt;xref target="section-anchor"&gt;reference text&lt;/xref&gt;: <xref target="section-anchor">reference text</xref>
            </t>
            <t>&lt;xref format="counter" target="section-anchor"/&gt;: <xref format="counter" target="section-anchor"/>
            </t>
            <t>&lt;xref format="counter" target="section-anchor"&gt;reference text&lt;/xref&gt;: <xref format="counter" target="section-anchor">reference text</xref>
            </t>
            <t>&lt;xref format="title" target="section-anchor"/&gt;: <xref format="title" target="section-anchor"/>
            </t>
            <t>&lt;xref format="title" target="section-anchor"&gt;reference text&lt;/xref&gt;: <xref format="title" target="section-anchor">reference text</xref>
            </t>
            <t>&lt;xref format="none" target="section-anchor"/&gt;: <xref format="none" target="section-anchor"/>
            </t>
            <t>&lt;xref format="none" target="section-anchor"&gt;reference text&lt;/xref&gt;: <xref format="none" target="section-anchor">reference text</xref>
            </t>
            <t>&lt;xref format="default" target="section-anchor"/&gt;: <xref format="default" target="section-anchor"/>
            </t>
            <t>&lt;xref format="default" target="section-anchor"&gt;reference text&lt;/xref&gt;: <xref format="default" target="section-anchor">reference text</xref>
            </t>
         </section>
